  • Field Details

    • DEFAULT

      static final int DEFAULT
      The type of model returned. Default = the model that always predicts the mean of data set.
      See Also:
      • Constant Field Values

    • ORIGINAL

      static final int ORIGINAL
      The type of model returned. Original = the real model but without pruning. Often stored for comparison
